    <h1>Provisionamento e deploy</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>Esta =C3=A9 uma sugest=C3=A3o de passos necess=C3=A1rios para re=
alizar o setup/deploy do Vault e Consul.<br>A id=C3=A9ia =C3=A9 que o proce=
sso seja o mesmo para todos os ambientes, distinguindo-se apenas no "sizing=
" do backend de storage "consul".</p>
<h2 id=3D"Provisionamentoedeploy-Consul">Consul</h2>
<p>Backend de storage (key/value) de alta disponibilidade que armazenar=C3=
=A1 os dados operados pelo Vault.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Provisionamento (single node):&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p><a href=3D"https://www.consul.io/intro/getting-started/install.html" cla=
ss=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.consul.io/intro/getting-s=
tarted/install.html</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Provisionamento (cluster):</strong></p>
<p><a href=3D"https://www.consul.io/docs/guides/bootstrapping.html" class=
=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.consul.io/docs/guides/boots=
trapping.html</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Official docker image:&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://hub.docker.com/_/consul/"=
 class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://hub.docker.com/_/consul/<=
/a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Sizing por ambiente</strong>:</p>
<p>development: single node<br>qa: single node<br>production: quorum de 3 a=
 5 nodes operando em cluster</p>
<h2 id=3D"Provisionamentoedeploy-Vault">Vault</h2>
<p><strong>Provisionamento:</strong></p>
<p><a href=3D"https://www.vaultproject.io/docs/install/index.html" class=3D=
"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.vaultproject.io/docs/install/i=
ndex.html</a></p>
<p>Official docker image:&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://hub.docker.com/_/vault/" =
class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://hub.docker.com/_/vault/</a=
></p>
<p>Ansible plugin:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href=3D"https://github.com/jhaals/ansible-vault" class=3D"external-l=
ink" rel=3D"nofollow">https://github.com/jhaals/ansible-vault</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/ansible-modules-hashivault" cla=
ss=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://pypi.python.org/pypi/ansible-=
modules-hashivault</a></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p>Deploy:</p>
<p><strong>1. Subindo o server vault com uma configura=C3=A7=C3=A3o utiliza=
ndo como storage: consul, e listener: https (necess=C3=A1rio gerar certific=
ado ssl)</strong></p>
<p>Obs: opera=C3=A7=C3=A3o realizada na inst=C3=A2ncia onde o Vault rodar=
=C3=A1</p>
<pre><code>$ vault server -config=3Dvault-config.hcl</code></pre>
<pre>exemplo do arquivo "vault-config.hcl":<br><code><br></code></pre>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: js; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">storage "=
consul" {
  address =3D "127.0.0.1:8500"
  path =3D "realwave"
}
listener "tcp" {
  address =3D "127.0.0.1:8200"
  tls_cert_file =3D "/var/lib/vault/ssl/vault.crt"
  tls_key_file =3D "/var/lib/vault/ssl/vault.key"
}
disable_mlock =3D true</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<p>Sobre "disable_mlock":&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://www.vaultproject.io/docs/=
configuration/index.html#disable_mlock" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofo=
llow">https://www.vaultproject.io/docs/configuration/index.html#disable_mlo=
ck</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>2. Inicializando o cofre</strong></p>
<pre><code>$ vault init</code></pre>
<p>obs: Armazenar em local seguro as "unseal keys" e "initial root token" e=
xibidos na tela, pois eles nunca mais ser=C3=A3o exibidos e podem ser solic=
itadas num eventual restart do vault.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>3. Destravando o cofre</strong></p>
<pre><code>$ vault unseal</code></pre>
<p>obs: Deve-se informar 3 das 5 "unseal keys" geradas no passo 2.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>4. Exportando o endere=C3=A7o do vault e o root token como vari=
=C3=A1vel de ambiente</strong>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Obs: At=C3=A9 o passo 3, n=C3=A3o foi necess=C3=A1rio autentica=C3=A7=C3=
=A3o, mas daqui pra frente ser=C3=A1 necess=C3=A1rio exportar o endere=C3=
=A7o do vault e o token root gerado no passado 2.</p>
<pre><code>$ export VAULT_ADDR=3D"https://[ip]:[port]"</code></pre>
<pre><code>$ export VAULT_TOKEN=3D"[initial root token]"</code></pre>
<pre><br></pre>
<p><strong>5. Habilitando a auditoria, s=C3=A3o 3 opc=C3=A7=C3=B5es: file, =
syslog e socket (<a href=3D"https://www.vaultproject.io/docs/audit" class=
=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.vaultproject.io/docs/audit<=
/a>)</strong></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>6. Invalidanto o root token por motivos de seguran=C3=A7a</stron=
g></p>
<pre><code>$ vault token-revoke "&lt;token&gt;"</code></pre>
<p>obs: Onde &lt;token&gt; deve ser substituido pelo "initial root token" g=
erado no passo 2.</p>
<p>obs2: Em caso de necessidade de alterar/incluir configura=C3=A7=C3=B5es =
administrativas, =C3=A9 poss=C3=ADvel gerar um outro root-token a partir da=
s chaves de unseal:&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://www.vaultproject.io/guides/gene=
rate-root.html" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.vaultp=
roject.io/guides/generate-root.html</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Documenta=C3=A7=C3=A3o de apoio:</p>
<p class=3D"auto-cursor-target"><a href=3D"https://www.vaultproject.io/intr=
o/getting-started/deploy.html" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">htt=
ps://www.vaultproject.io/intro/getting-started/deploy.html</a><br><a href=
=3D"https://www.vaultproject.io/guides/production.html" class=3D"external-l=
ink" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.vaultproject.io/guides/production.html</a=
></p>
